70
00:05:02,395 --> 00:05:03,195
And they're the kind of partners

71
00:05:03,215 --> 00:05:04,555
that you might want to think about

72
00:05:04,595 --> 00:05:07,235
whether it's actually a good business decision for you

73
00:05:07,576 --> 00:05:09,356
or your studio or your game going forward.

74
00:05:11,257 --> 00:05:13,198
Other factors might include the budget you're asking for.

75
