00:29:29,233 --> 00:29:31,194
and that prevents you from doing certain things,

508
00:29:31,695 --> 00:29:33,555
then your publisher should be able to justify

509
00:29:33,595 --> 00:29:35,776
exactly how they want to use the rights they're taking.

510
00:29:36,918 --> 00:29:39,899
So some additional things to check through

511
00:29:40,399 --> 00:29:43,200
in respect of a publishing license scope are as follows.

