00:30:05,207 --> 00:30:07,789
or thinks that a game might turn into a franchise,

520
00:30:08,149 --> 00:30:10,451
then there's a couple of developer-friendly ways

521
00:30:11,152 --> 00:30:11,872
to go about this.

