via the GDC site and you can find the written articles on my Contract Killer series available

934
00:55:57,263 --> 00:56:02,587
on Gamasutra to read for free, so please check those out. I hope you found this session useful

935
00:56:03,007 --> 00:56:06,870
and have more confidence going into your negotiations with the publisher that it's okay to change

936
00:56:06,910 --> 00:56:08,011
certain things in your contract.

937
